title: Ambulance Quality Indicators
description: This contains background material for the Ambulance System Indicators (AmbSYS) and Clinical Outcomes (AmbCO) for all eleven Ambulance Services in England.
datasetNotes: On the landing page scroll down to the 'Time series data' for XLS or 'CSV data' for CSV and click on the latest release.
sizingNotes: A number of messy tables with footnotes
notes: Although not specifically Covid-19  the spreadsheets may allow the impact of the pandemic to be derived.
